data.description: Excellent Investor/Developer Opportunity To Acquire Tear down Property Consisting of Three Large City Lots Totaling 11,250 Sq/Ft (Lots 7, 8, & 9 = Lot 808 in Square 6093) in a Park-Setting, with Convenient Rear Off-Street Driveway Parking for up to 12 cars or more.  Property has an existing Salvageable All Brick, 2-Story Cape Cod, 4-Bedrooms, 2-Bathrooms, with Finished Basement, Large Rear Wood Deck and Driveway.   Currently Zoned R-2 which can accommodate (3) Single Family Houses, or (2) Sets of Semi-Detached Townhouses, or (1) Single Family House + (1) Set of Semi-Detached Townhouses all with their own off-street parking.  By simply, petitioning DC RA for the change to R-3 Zoning, this property can possibly accommodate (5) Row Townhouses all with off street parking as well.    Conveniently located in Congress Heights Neighborhood near the following:   1-Block from the Metro Bus Line 1-Mile from the Congress Heights Metro Station 1-Mile from the Department of Homeland Security Headquarters@ St. Elizabeth’s Campus 1-Miles from Joint Base Anacostia-Bolling 1-Mile from the DC Entertainment & Sport Arena ¼- Mile to/from I-295 North & South
